OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fdry with low cloud and fog patches
OL,9,Facross the east. Chilly in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FMisty low cloud burning
OL,12,Fback to the east coast. Otherwise it
OL,13,Fwill be dry and sunny. Very warm or
OL,14,Fhot but cooler along eastern coastal
OL,15,Fdistricts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
