OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fand sunny on Thursday and Friday but
OL,7,Feast and north coasts may be cloudier.
OL,8,FDry on Saturday but cloudier than of
OL,9,Flate. Very warm Thursday, then turning
OL,10,Fcooler.
